lead_paragraph: Authorities say an 83-year-old Arizona man accused of killing a Texas teacher and ex-beauty queen when he was a young priest in 1960 is set to be extradited to Texas.

headline.main: Man to Be Extradited to Texas for 1960 Death of Beauty Queen
